<PageTitle>Task list</PageTitle>

<span class="govuk-caption-xl">Components</span>
<h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Task list</h1>

<p class="govuk-body">
    A blazor implementation of the GDS <a href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/components/task-list/" class="govuk-link">Task list</a>.
</p>

