<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="how-it-works">How it works</h2>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m" id="task-title">Task title or name</h3>
<p class="govuk-body">All tasks must have a title or name to give the user reasonable expectation of what the task is about. Use sentence case and keep it short.</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m" id="common-task-statuses">Common task statuses</h3>
<p class="govuk-body">
    All tasks must have a short descriptor to give the users a quick overview of how much they have completed and how much is left to do. Most statuses use coloured tags and there are a set of common statuses to ensure consistent wording.
</p>
<h3 class="govuk-heading-m" id="task-link">A link to the task page</h3>
<p class="govuk-body">All tasks have a link to a page where users can start the task.</p>

