<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="complete-multiple-tasks">Completing multiple task lists</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
    If there are a lot of tasks to complete, grouping them into multiple lists makes it easier for users to understand and plan what they need to do. See <a href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/patterns/complete-multiple-tasks/" class="govuk-link">complete multiple tasks pattern</a> @*showcase*@ for more details.
</p>

